1
00:00:00,280 --> 00:00:06,480
One time I came out here
while I was shackled with a chain

2
00:00:07,320 --> 00:00:11,919
I was sick, and they brought a doctor to examine me. I looked and saw my mother

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Sitting in our house's courtyard. That is my family's main house

4
00:00:14,519 --> 00:00:18,039
This is my family's main house. I looked and saw my mother over there

5
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:21,719
She was praying the noon prayer in the courtyard

6
00:00:28,199 --> 00:00:29,839
This is my family's main house

7
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:44,280
The woman sitting in the courtyard over there is my mother

8
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:48,560
Before, when I saw her while I was shackled with a chain

9
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:51,679
I saw her sitting in the same area or close to it
